"before the Cataclysm, by OmniCorp. It is more formidable than the size of "
"its .22 rounds would suggest."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG DBR"
msgid_plural "OCG DBR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"Over and under Double Barrel Revolver with 12 rounds. Its cylinder has six "
"pairs of over/under chambers aligned with the barrels. Such was OmniCorp's "
"solution to improve the stopping power of .22 ETC in a revolver."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json .\items\gun\9etc.json .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid "double"
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG SMP"
msgid_plural "OCG SMP"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"Designed as a dedicated \"silent\" gun by OmniCorp, The Stealth Machine "
"Pistol is an electrothermal-chemical .22 pistol with an integrated "
"suppressor. A valuable sidearm for covert operatives."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG Stealth Pistol"
msgid_plural "OCG Stealth Pistol"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp Stealth Pistol is surprisingly small even with an integrated "
"suppressor. Made only with composite ceramics and polymers to bypass metal "
"detectors when unloaded at the expense of reliability, a now useless "
"feature."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid "M2010 ESR"
msgid_plural "M2010 ESR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid "OCG SMC300"
msgid_plural "OCG SMC300s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid ""
"Stockless Marksman Carbine, the first gun among OmniCorp products, is a "
"selective-fire \"sidearm\" which shares magazines with sniper rifles. "
"Includes critically needed gyroscopic stabilizer. This .300 WM version won "
"three \"Overkill Awards\" from the Guns n Ammo magazine."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\308.json
msgid "OCG SMC308"
msgid_plural "OCG SMC308s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\308.json
msgid ""
"Stockless Marksman Carbine, the first gun among OmniCorp products, is a "
"selective-fire \"sidearm\" which shares magazines with sniper rifles. "
"Includes critically needed gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ADR"
msgid_plural "OCG ADR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"The Anti-Drone Revolver is an OmniCorp \"sidearm\" with a carbine length "
"barrel and overcharged electrothermal action, designed to defeat the "
"heaviest among armored drones. Comes with a classic finish in wood."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The base model on its own is a highly accurate battle rifle "
"with a \"pulsed\" two-round burst mode. Supports aftermarket modifications, "
"but using its conversion kits instead is advised."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-ADS"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-ADS"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Anti-Drone Sniper features an overcharged electrothermal "
"action. Comes with integrated forward grip/bipod unit, gyroscopic stabilizer"
" and cheek pad."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-CAR"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-CAR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Carbine supports automatic fire, has an integrated recoil"
" stock and foregrip, with room for one more underbarrel accessory."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-CQB"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-CQB"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Close Quarters Battle variant supports automatic fire, "
"comes with integrated recoil stock, underbarrel laser sight and RM42I "
"bayonet."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-SAW"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-SAW"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Squad Automatic Weapon supports ammo belts, has a "
"reinforced barrel, a very high rate of fire and comes with integrated "
"forward grip/bipod unit, recoil stock, ported barrel and gyroscopic "
"stabilizer."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-SR"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-SR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. Not that accurate or long ranged for a Sniper Rifle, but "
"unlike most, has a two-round burst mode. Comes with integrated forward "
"grip/bipod unit, gyroscopic stabilizer and cheek pad."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-UDD"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-UDD"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Urban Drone Destroyer is very powerful, fast firing but "
"difficult to control in full auto. Comes with integrated recoil stock, "
"ported barrel and gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG AMR"
msgid_plural "OCG AMR"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp's Anti-Materiel Revolver might be the most powerful handgun ever "
"made. It can destroy almost anything within four shots, but its recoil is so"
" heavy its manual forbids shooting it without wearing power armor."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG DWOM"
msgid_plural "OCG DWOM"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"A battle rifle for future warfare scenarios involving long range "
"engagements, power armor and tank drones, the highly accurate Drone Warfare "
"Opus Magnum can fire two-round bursts of hypervelocity 7.62x51mm EC rounds."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG MAR7k"
msgid_plural "OCG MAR7k"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"Considered an overkill among overkills, the bullpup Mega Assault Rifle is "
"the most powerful fully automatic rifle of OmniCorp. Even with fixed "
"foregrip and bipod, it is very compact due to a \"CQB\" barrel, a receiver "
"shortened through a vertically sliding bolt and a magazine well right next "
"to its buttplate."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG OFG16k"
msgid_plural "OCG OFG16ks"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"The Orbital Force Gun is an anti-materiel light-gas rifle with a detachable,"
" vacuum-sealable barrel which can be connected to a hydrogen canister yet "
"works without one with drastically reduced muzzle energy. Its manual "
"recommends avoiding hydrogen despite that due to reliability issues a future"
" OFG16kA1 model would solve."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG Seven-7B"
msgid_plural "OCG Seven-7B"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"Electrothermal magazine-fed bolt-action anti-materiel rifle. Its "
"hypervelocity 7.62x51mm EC round is not as damaging as a conventional .50 "
"BMG, but its recoil is much lower and its armor penetration better."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Desert Eel"
msgid_plural "OCG Desert Eel"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"This electrothermal-chemical pistol packs a lot of power for its size and "
"weight. As an UPS cannot fit inside a pocket, OmniCorp Desert Eel is a true "
"pocket pistol only for cyborgs with the UPS bionic."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Hand Autocannon"
msgid_plural "OCG Hand Autocannons"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Bulky, heavy and intimidating, the Hand Autocannon is the most powerful "
"electrothermal-chemical pistol developed by OmniCorp. It has 2 round burst "
"and automatic fire modes."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG N9A1 Chaingun"
msgid_plural "OCG N9A1 Chainguns"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp biggest \"minigun\" stands out from the Nanogun with its unique "
"trigger group and very flexible burst limiter. Each setting in its fire "
"selector lever can be further tuned through short or long trigger pulls."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038H"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038Hs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"9mm ETC variant of OmniCorp O2038 SMG. Features more stopping power, recoil,"
" louder gunfire, reduced rate of fire and less rounds per magazine. Utilizes"
" a helical magazine to maximize ammunition capacity."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038HSD"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038HSDs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"A 9mm ETC version of the O2038SD with a heavier suppressor, developed "
"together with depleted uranium 9x19mm subsonic armor-piercing rounds. When "
"firing such rounds, it is quieter than the O2038SD, but much louder "
"otherwise"
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O9 Electromagnum"
msgid_plural "OCG O9 Electromagnum"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"An electrothermal-chemical revolver from OmniCorp, capable of firing eight "
"9mm bullets at high velocities. Comparable to a .44 magnum or .460 Rowland "
"revolver in performance, but requires a charged UPS."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O9-2 Doublemag"
msgid_plural "OCG O9-2 Doublemag"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"A double-barreled yet compact 9mm electrothermal-chemical revolver from "
"OmniCorp. Unlike the .22 DBR, its layout and action allow single shots but "
"impairs accuracy and makes it less reliable."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "single"
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG MS400 Mini Sniper"
msgid_plural "OCG MS400 Mini Sniper"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Propelling rounds at muzzle velocities expected from rifle cartridges, this "
"highly accurate 9mm electrothermal-chemical rifle from OmniCorp can mostly "
"fulfill the sniper role in urban environments."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG MS400SD Boatman"
msgid_plural "OCG MS400SD Boatman"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"This variant of the MS400 Mini Sniper is deadly accurate and \"silent\" even"
" with hypersonic rounds. A great OmniCorp product for 6'+ tall bald hitmen "
"or zombie apocalypse survivors."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Super SMG"
msgid_plural "OCG Super SMGs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"\"Puts the machinegun in submachinegun\" - OmniCorp marketing pitch. "
"Compatible with ammo belts, the SSMG is very bulky but can almost match a "
"5.56x45mm machinegun's stopping power. Features integrated combined forward "
"grip/bipod unit and a roomy magazine well."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG Baby Eel"
msgid_plural "OCG Baby Eels"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"Externally almost identical to the electrothermal Desert Eel, this pocket "
"pistol is very lightweight, but felt recoil is higher than in most 9mm "
"pistols."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9 DMSMG"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9 DMSMG"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp MR9 is called a Designated Marksman Submachinegun. It has a very "
"long, match-grade barrel and a highly accurate action. Technically a "
"submachinegun, it resembles and is handled like a rifle."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9S Mini Rifle"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9S Mini Rifle"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"A civilian, semi-automatic version of OmniCorp MR9 DMSMG with the same very "
"long barrel. Some call it a carbine despite its barrel length, others call "
"it a rifle. Either way, it is good for what it is but expensive."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9SD Styx"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9SD Styx"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"Without requiring subsonic rounds and with the same length as the MR9 DMSMG,"
" OmniCorp Styx is a pretty \"silent\" firearm. Weaker and shorter ranged "
"than a rifle caliber one like the VSS Vintorez, it still is useful for "
"covert marksmen."
msgstr ""

